      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong>,<strong> </strong>2/3 of the <strong>grated garlic</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>sugar </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until softened and beginning to caramelise</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1670930185823-x200.jpg",
