            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once slightly softened, add your <strong>tomato paste</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min, then add 80ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[90ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> and reduce the heat to medium</p><p>Add your <strong>blanched peas</strong>,<strong> </strong>give everything a good mix up and cook for 2 min or until warmed through – this is your <strong>spiced veggie mixture</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
