      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked, stir through your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>yellow rice</strong> to the spiced veggie mixture<strong> </strong>and mix it all together until fully combined – this is your <strong>smoky Spanish-style pepper & pea rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
